<p align="justify"><span color="#202020" style="color: #202020;"><span face="Verdana, serif" style="font-family: Verdana, serif;"><span><b><span>Al final de la negociación tenemos que pagar 12.000:</span></b></span></span></span></p>
<table cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" style="width: 592px;"><colgroup><col width="464" /> <col width="46" /> <col width="50" /> </colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td width="464" bgcolor="#e6e6e6">
<p align="center"><span color="#202020" style="color: #202020;"><span face="Verdana, serif" style="font-family: Verdana, serif;"><span><b>CONCEPTO</b></span></span></span></p>
